Sam Brownback is set to become
U.S. ambassador-at-large for

04:03.466 --> 04:04.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
religious freedom.

04:04.966 --> 04:07.033 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
