has plummeted over steep tax
cuts that led to severe budget

04:12.733 --> 04:15.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
problems in Kansas.

04:15.300 --> 04:19.000 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
